(Real-time whiteboard synchronisation relies on an event-driven WebSocket protocol. When a) Tj
T* (teacher moves a page index, the SDK emits a scene-change event that propagates to all) Tj
T* (participants in the room within milliseconds. Participants poll the shared scene state at) Tj
T* (1-second intervals to handle reconnection scenarios. A PDF document uploaded before) Tj
T* (session start is converted to a series of whiteboard scenes, each corresponding to one page,) Tj
T* (enabling seamless teacher-controlled navigation.) Tj
